title: YouTube takes down, then reinstates John Ondrasik video that criticized Biden Afghanistan withdrawal
description: A music video written by famed singer-songwriter John Ondrasik titled "Blood on my Hands" went viral this week before being removed and then reinstated on YouTube Friday.
